{"tid":2032051,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港其實係一個悲情城巿","createTime":"2020-05-23T22:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T00:03:50.000Z","uid":138752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"397879950124050a1cb205c25c230f160a236cf5","tid":2032051,"uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:11:31.000Z","msg":"貧富懸殊世界第一 <br />\n樓價世界第一 拋離新加坡一倍<br />\n人均居住面積十三平方米 遠低於美國等發達國家<br />\n210000人住劏房 人均居住面積僅僅大過一張乒乓波枱<br />\n<br />\nGDP世界第十二 <br />\n工時世界頭三 <br />\n但人工比廿五年前小咗一成<br />\n<br />\n每五人有一人有ptsd/depression 傾向<br />\n同經歷咗 天災 恐襲 武裝衝突嘅地區差唔多<br />\n<br />\n未講近一年發生嘅社會事件 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a382d42504d9ec16e67640ad9e0b59246c58f7e8","tid":2032051,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:16:37.000Z","msg":"呢個term我讀中學個陣已經聽緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dc1946fb31d9ae08a8715d0ec3c880a557c13d","tid":2032051,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:16:49.000Z","msg":"世界仲有地方打緊仗 飢荒 <br />\n<br />\n世界末日最好 一切重新修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdab48677bd80d55dd7df56ab367b7b9ce654c0c","tid":2032051,"uid":138752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13dc1946fb31d9ae08a8715d0ec3c880a557c13d","tid":2032051,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:16:49.000Z","msg":"世界仲有地方打緊仗 飢荒 <br />\n<br />\n世界末日最好 一切重新修正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T22:20:48.000Z","msg":"如果嗰個地方打緊仗而又係世界第七不快樂國家，我會覺得正常 <br />\n但香港gdp世界前列 而且唔會有飢荒發生 <br />\n但係世界第七不快樂 就好有問題"},{"pid":"b941da605578fddd0d5136be7f4c4ebc22c1df4a","tid":2032051,"uid":332452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T00:03:50.000Z","msg":"香港本身係難民城市"}]}